---
import SectionContainer from "@/components/SectionContainer.astro";
import ProfileCheck from "@/icons/ProfileCheck.astro";
---

<SectionContainer id="about">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
    <h2 class="text-4xl opacity-70">About me</h2>
    <ProfileCheck />
  </div>
  <div class="text-pretty text-xl max-w-xl gap-y-6 flex flex-col">
    <p class="font-semibold">
      My name is
      <span class="text-aqua2 dark:text-aqua/80">Maximo Dip Aparicio</span>
      but my friends call me Dip. I started programming about 5 years ago, when i
      was 15.
    </p>
    <p class="font-semibold">
      I've been
      <span class="text-aqua2 dark:text-aqua/80"> developing projects</span>
      while doing my university carrer as a programmer. Those are the ones you can
      see above, on the
      <i>projects</i>
      section.
    </p>
    <p class="font-semibold">
      At the moment, i'm
      <span class="text-aqua2 dark:text-aqua/80">
        looking for new opportunities.</span
      >
      My goals are to improve my skills as a developer, learning new technologies
      and creating great software.
    </p>
  </div>
</SectionContainer>
